        <abstract> 
<p>Sends a copy of A. R. Wallace’s work [<hi rend="italic">The geographical distribution of animals</hi> (1876)].</p> 
            <p>Advises Fd’AF on how to carry out his work, "Keep notes &amp; go on accumulating facts". CD will write to J. D. Hooker about the plants Fd’AF has collected.</p>
        </abstract>
